# Dependency Visualizer

A tool to visualize Python project dependencies using [Tach](https://github.com/PolicyEngine/tach).

## Features

*   Renders interactive dependency graphs.
*   Highlights dependencies and dependees of selected modules.
*   Allows drilling down into module subdirectories (exploding).
*   Supports collapsing exploded views.

## Installation

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/dependency-visualizer.git # Replace with your repo URL
cd dependency-visualizer

# Install the package and dependencies
pip install .
```

## Usage

```bash
depviz
```

Then, select the root directory of your Python project. 
